Diagrams & OPL

SD

OPL

  • 1. Security of Compliance can be not ok or ok.
  • 2. Integrity is stateful.
  • 3. Confidentiality is stateful.
  • 4. Availability can be not ok or ok.
  • 5. Intellectual Property Confidentiality can be not ok or ok.
  • 6. Response Integrity can be not ok or ok.
  • 7. Non Repudiation can be not ok or ok.
  • 8. Accountability can be not ok or ok.
  • 9. Security consists of Availability, Confidentiality, and Integrity.
  • 10. Confidentiality consists of Data Protection and Intellectual Property Confidentiality and four more parts.
  • 11. Trustworthiness consists of Availability and Security.
  • 12. AI Agent exhibits Intellectual Property Confidentiality with value not ok, Accountability with value not ok, and Response Integrity with value not ok.
  • 13. Processing exhibits Intellectual Property Confidentiality with value not ok, Availability with value not ok, Response Integrity with value not ok, and Accountability with value not ok.
  • 14. Integrity consists of Non Repudiation and Response Integrity and 16 more parts.
  • 15. Processing exhibits Non Repudiation with value ok.
  • 16. Non Repudiation consists of Accountability.
  • 17. Compliance exhibits Security.
  • 18. Cloud Based AI Agent and On Prem AI Agent are AI Agents.
  • 19. Cloud Based AI Agent exhibits Availability with value not ok.
  • 20. Jailbreak, Prompt Injection, and Sensitive Information Disclosure and three more specializations are Threats.
  • 21. AI Agent and Human Agent are Process Resources.
  • 22. Recruiting For A Position is Processing.
  • 23. Cloud Based AI Agent handles Processing.
  • 24. Processing yields Intellectual Property Confidentiality at state not ok.

Back to Top

SD1: Recruiting For A Position in-zoomed

OPL

  • 1. Recruiting For A Position from SD zooms in SD1 into Receiving Applications, Selecting Top Applications, and ..., which occur in that time sequence.
  • 2. Intellectual Property Confidentiality can be not ok or ok.
  • 3. Response Integrity can be not ok or ok.
  • 4. Availability can be not ok or ok.
  • 5. Confidentiality can be not ok or ok.
  • 6. Integrity can be not ok or ok.
  • 7. Application can be accepted, rejected or submitted.
  • 8. AI Agent and Human Agent are Process Resources.
  • 9. Cloud Based AI Agent and On Prem AI Agent are AI Agents.
  • 10. Confidentiality consists of Intellectual Property Confidentiality and five more parts.
  • 11. Specific AI Agent consists of Function Calling Element, LLM Model, and Memory Element.
  • 12. Specific AI Agent is a Cloud Based AI Agent.
  • 13. Specific AI Agent exhibits Intellectual Property Confidentiality with value not ok and Response Integrity with value not ok.
  • 14. Embedding Extraction, Prompt Injection, Sensitive Information Disclosure, and Tool Misuse and two more specializations are Threats.
  • 15. LLM Model is subject to Prompt Injection and Sensitive Information Disclosure.
  • 16. Sensitive Information Disclosure results state not ok of Intellectual Property Confidentiality.
  • 17. Prompt Injection results state not ok of Response Integrity.
  • 18. Selecting Top Applications exhibits Response Integrity with value ok.
  • 19. Receiving Applications exhibits Intellectual Property Confidentiality with value ok.
  • 20. Integrity consists of Response Integrity and 17 more parts.
  • 21. Memory Element is subject to Embedding Extraction.
  • 22. Function Calling Element is subject to Tool Misuse.
  • 23. Specific Human Role is a Human Agent.
  • 24. Specific AI Agent handles Receiving Applications.
  • 25. Receiving Applications yields Application at state submitted.
  • 26. Specific AI Agent and Specific Human Role handle Selecting Top Applications.
  • 27. Selecting Top Applications requires Application at state submitted.
  • 28. Selecting Top Applications yields Application at one of the states accepted or rejected.

Back to Top

SD2: Recruiting For A Position unfolded

OPL

  • 1. Recruiting For A Position from SD part-unfolds in SD2 into ..., Receiving Applications, and Selecting Top Applications.
  • 2. Recruiting For A Position consists of Receiving Applications, Selecting Top Applications, and in that sequence....
  • 3. Recruiting For A Position is Processing.

Back to Top

SD3: View of AI Threats and Security Objectives

OPL

  • 1. SD3 is a view OPD, derived from SD.
  • 2. Confidentiality can be not ok or ok.
  • 3. Availability can be not ok or ok.
  • 4. Integrity can be not ok or ok.
  • 5. Response Integrity can be not ok or ok.
  • 6. Non Repudiation can be not ok or ok.
  • 7. Embedding Extraction, Extortion by AI Agent, Jailbreak, Prompt Injection, Sensitive Information Disclosure, and Tool Misuse are Threats.
  • 8. Integrity consists of Authenticity, Buffer Space Integrity, Content Integrity, External Configuration & Environment Trustfulness, File Integrity, Hardware Non-interference, Input Processing Correctness, Interface Integrity, Network Infrastructure Integrity, Non Repudiation, Pointer Integrity, Predictability Of Multi-step User Inputs, Resource Trustfulness, Response Integrity, Shared Resource Integrity, Supply Chain Integrity, User State Information Integrity, and Zero Race Condition.
  • 9. Confidentiality consists of Interaction Only With Trusted Entities, Opacity, Sensitive Information Untraceability, and System Property Untraceability and two more parts.
  • 10. Availability consists of Deadlock Freeness, Engaging Time Controllability, Resource Allocation Moderation, Resource Controllability, and Zero Source Leak.
  • 11. Authorization consists of Authentication Mechanism Faultlessness, Authentication Unavoidability, Physical Protection, and Privilege Preservation.
